<p>
    <em>Goo Create</em> was an in-browser and cloud based <em>WebGL/HTML5</em> creative tool that allows you to materialize interactive 3D scenes that work in all modern devices.
</p>
<p>
    My responsibilities were to design the product interface under the direction of <em>Magnus Östergren</em> (COO) but also took up the development/maintenance of the site, user onboarding, and social media.
</p>

