<h2>The Process</h2>

<p>
    Designing the interface and creating intuitive user flows was a gradual and iterative process. At <em>Goo Create</em>, we streamlined a process around user feedback, proposed solution concept, interactive wireframes (using UXPin), high fidelity mockups in <em> Adobe Illustrator</em> with as many iterations as possible and finally the actual implementation.
</p>

